{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/kolaborasi-unik-dc-comics-injustice-vs-he-man-and-the-masters-of-the-universe/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Kolaborasi Unik DC Comics: Injustice vs He-Man and the Masters of the Universe","content":"<p>DC Comics, sebagai satu dari <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dc-comics-vs-marvel-comics-dua-tetangga-yang-jarang-akur/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">dua penguasa bisnis buku komik superheroes dunia</a>, tentu memiliki banyak judul dan serial di bawah bendera mereka.</p>\n<p>Mulai dari <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/merayakan-action-comics-edisi-ke-1000-kenapa-superman-celana-dalamnya-di-depan-ini-jawabannya/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Action Comics</em></a> sampai Justice League; hampir seluruh produk komik DC Comics memiliki pangsa pasar yang baik walau bersama Marvel saat ini <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mirip-dc-comics-rebirth-marvel-comics-meluncurkan-fresh-start/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">DC Comics memang sedang tidak berada dalam kondisi terbaik</a> mereka di bisnis komik. Namun kondisi yang kurang bagus tidak membuat DC Comics kehilangan akal maupun kreativitas. Mereka terus berusaha melakukan inovasi-inovasi demi mendongkrak volume penjualan buku komik DC. Salah satu cara yang digunakan adalah membuat kolaborasi. Bekerja sama dengan pemegang IP populer lain.</p>\n<p>Hal itu terlihat dari kolaborasi DC Comics dengan IP terkenal lain. Setelah dulu ada Scooby Doo “Scooby Apocalypse” dari Hanna-Barbera (dengan <em>art</em> dari seniman top DC Jim Lee), kini mari bersiap-siap menyambut “<em>Injustice vs He-Man and the Masters of the Universe</em>” dari pabrik mainan besar Mattel.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46861\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46861\" data-attachment-id=\"46861\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kolaborasi-unik-dc-comics-injustice-vs-he-man-and-the-masters-of-the-universe/attachment/heman7-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman7-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber gambar: Scoobypedia\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber gambar: Scoobypedia&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman7-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman7-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46861\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman7-1.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber gambar: Scoobypedia\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman7-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman7-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46861\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: Scoobypedia</p></div></p>\n<p>Sebenarnya He-Man bukan tokoh asing di DC Universe, karena komik DC “<em>He-Man and the Masters of the Universe</em>” sudah pernah diterbitkan pada tahun 2012. Kali ini He-Man berkolaborasi dengan karakter DC Universe lain di <em>storyline “Injustice</em>” yang kontroversial.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46857\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46857\" data-attachment-id=\"46857\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kolaborasi-unik-dc-comics-injustice-vs-he-man-and-the-masters-of-the-universe/attachment/heman3-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman3-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber gambar: Wikia\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber gambar: Wikia&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman3-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman3-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46857\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman3-1.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber gambar: Wikia\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman3-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman3-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46857\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: Wikia</p></div></p>\n<p>Serial <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/injustice-saat-superman-kehilangan-akal-sehat-dan-menjadi-diktator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Injustice</a> adalah serial komik DC yang dibuat sebagai <em>background story video game</em> dari Netherrealm Studio. Mungkin awalnya tidak direncanakan sebagai serial panjang dengan kontinuitas, namun serial Injustice ternyata disukai hingga terbit sampai <em>Year Five</em> hingga sekarang.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46860\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46860\" data-attachment-id=\"46860\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kolaborasi-unik-dc-comics-injustice-vs-he-man-and-the-masters-of-the-universe/attachment/heman6-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman6-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber gambar: Bailedosenxutos\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber gambar: Bailedosenxutos&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman6-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman6-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46860\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman6-1.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber gambar: Bailedosenxutos\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman6-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman6-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46860\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: Bailedosenxutos</p></div></p>\n<p>Jadi ada dimana posisi <em>Injustice vs He-Man and the Masters of the Universe</em>” di <em>universe Injustice</em>?</p>\n<p><em>Sepertinya ada di ‘alternate univers</em>e’. Tapi masih memiliki keterikatan dengan komik <em>canonical Injustice</em>. Masih berada dalam <em>universe Injustice</em>. Dan Superman masih seorang diktator sialan yang mengangkat dirinya sebagai Tuhan untuk umat manusia.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46856\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46856\" data-attachment-id=\"46856\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kolaborasi-unik-dc-comics-injustice-vs-he-man-and-the-masters-of-the-universe/attachment/heman2-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman2-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Diktator dari Planet Krypton. Sumber gambar: Polygon\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Diktator dari Planet Krypton. Sumber gambar: Polygon&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman2-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman2-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46856\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman2-1.jpg\" alt=\"Diktator dari Planet Krypton. Sumber gambar: Polygon\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman2-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman2-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46856\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Diktator dari Planet Krypton. Sumber gambar: Polygon</p></div></p>\n<p>Dan itu memang benang merah di semua inkarnasi Injustice; baik di buku komik maupun di <em>video game</em>.</p>\n<p>Di Injustice, Superman adalah si brengsek yang mengubah tata dunia. Dari independen demokrasi menjadi totalitarian diktatorisme. Dengan alasan keamanan dan ketertiban dunia, Superman mengambil alih pemerintahan Amerika (dan dunia) ke tangannya sendiri. Sebuah skenario “apa yang terjadi jika Superman, makhluk terkuat di dunia, memutuskan menjadi seorang diktator?”. Semua terjadi akibat rasa marah dan sedih kehilangan istri dan anak yang dikandung istrinya akibat ulah The Joker.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46859\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46859\" data-attachment-id=\"46859\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kolaborasi-unik-dc-comics-injustice-vs-he-man-and-the-masters-of-the-universe/attachment/heman5-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman5-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Superman yang menakutkan. Sumber gambar: Pinterest\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Superman yang menakutkan. Sumber gambar: Pinterest&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman5-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman5-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46859\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman5-1.jpg\" alt=\"Superman yang menakutkan. Sumber gambar: Pinterest\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman5-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman5-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46859\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Superman yang menakutkan. Sumber gambar: Pinterest</p></div></p>\n<p><em>Injustice vs He-Man and the Masters of the Universe</em> akan terdiri dari enam volume buku dan akan bercerita soal Batman yang berasal dari <em>alternate-reality</em> Injustice universe bekerja sama dengan Prince Adam aka. He-Man, Teela, Orko dan Battlecat dari Eternia (belum ada indikasi kehadiran Man-At-Arms) untuk menghadapi Superman.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46858\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46858\" data-attachment-id=\"46858\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kolaborasi-unik-dc-comics-injustice-vs-he-man-and-the-masters-of-the-universe/attachment/heman4-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman4-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber gambar: Polygon\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber gambar: Polygon&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman4-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman4-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46858\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman4-1.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber gambar: Polygon\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman4-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman4-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46858\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: Polygon</p></div></p>\n<p>Dari sinopsis resmi yang dirilis pihak DC Comics disebutkan kalau “setelah membebaskan kerajaannya dari cengkeraman robot, Prince Adam kedatangan pengunjung dari dimensi lain yang meminta bantuan untuk mengalahkan mantan superhero yang berubah menjadi diktator. Dia setuju untuk membantu. He-Man bersama rekan-rekan setianya dari Eternia dan sekutu baru dari dimensi asing, Batman, akan menghadapi bahaya baru serta musuh-musuh familiar dimana kini tidak ada dunia dan dimensi yang aman dari diktator dan kejahatan”.</p>\n<p>Komik miniseri “Injustice vs He-Man and the Masters of the Universe” ini naskahnya ditulis oleh Tim Seeley. Seeley sebelumnya menulis cerita untuk komik “<em>Nightwing</em>” dan “<em>Green Lanterns”</em>. Untuk grafis akan ditangani oleh illustrator yang sebelumnya menangani “<em>He-Man/Thundercats</em>” serta “<em>Batman/Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles</em>”, yaitu Freddie E. Williams II. <em>Personally,</em> saya penasaran gimana hasilnya kalau ilustrasi ditangani mantan<em> penciler</em> DC Comics, Ardian Syaf? Tapi sepertinya itu mustahil untuk terjadi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46855\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46855\" data-attachment-id=\"46855\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kolaborasi-unik-dc-comics-injustice-vs-he-man-and-the-masters-of-the-universe/attachment/heman1-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman1-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Batman/Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles. Sumber gambar: DC Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Batman/Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles. Sumber gambar: DC Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman1-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman1-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46855\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman1-1.jpg\" alt=\"Batman/Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles. Sumber gambar: DC Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman1-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/heman1-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46855\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Batman/Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles. Sumber gambar: DC Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Dengan adanya Injustice terbaru di luar Injustice canonical, bisa dikatakan kalau serial Injustice masih akan bertahan lama di pasaran. Kita lihat saja apakah benar seperti itu atau tidak? Komik Injustice vs He-Man and the Masters of the Universe mulai terbit 18 Juli 2018.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"c8e1f5b3-16a9-5d91-a4ec-c14a9f015a1a"}}}